T1  - Gender homophily: In-group citation preferences and the gender disadvantage
AU  - Zhou, Sifan
AU  - Chai, Sen
AU  - Freeman, Richard B.
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
IS  - 1
SP  - 104895
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/01/01/
SN  - 0048-7333
